<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>E-Learning Activation code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        strong {
            color: #28a745;
        }

        .welcome-message {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="welcome-message">
            <h1>Welcome, <%= user.name%>!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for choosing Your App Name. We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        </div>
        <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is: <strong><%= activationCode%></strong></p>
        <p>This OTP is valid for the next 5 minutes. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us on E-Learning - LMS!</p>
        <footer>
            <p>Sent viaE-Learning</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
